        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://sysghent.be/events/showcase-projects/"/>
        <id>https://sysghent.be/events/showcase-projects/</id>
        
        <content type="html" xml:base="https://sysghent.be/events/showcase-projects/">&lt;p&gt;Do you have a cool personal project that you want to show? Let us know and we will give you a slot to present it. We will have a projector and a microphone available.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Those who are interested can join us for dinner at 18:30 in one of the restaurants nearby (TBA).&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</content>
        
